{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_01_02",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 2話 麻奈の妹",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……\nうん、新曲の振り付けいい感じ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff*\nThe choreography for the new song is great!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1666666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くんもそう思わない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t you agree‚ {user}?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、俺もいいと思ったよ\nあくまでも素人の意見だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Looks good to me.\nJust an amateur’s point of view tho.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "素人じゃないよ、{user}くんは私の\nプロのアイドル、長瀬麻奈の専属マネージャーでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh come on‚ don’t be so humble.\n{user}‚ you’re the main manager of the professional idol Mana Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "一応な\n三枝さんには迷惑掛けてばっかりだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess so.\nBut I’m always getting bailed out by Saegusa-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.433333333333337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、この前{user}くんのこと\n褒めてたよ。なかなか使い勝手のいいヤツだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He praised {user} the other day‚ you know.\nHe said you were pretty handy to have around.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ニュアンスが微妙だな……\nまぁ、役に立ってるならいいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds like a back-handed compliment…\nWell‚ I guess I should be glad to be of some use.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9391651749611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "もっと自信持ちなよ～。私がアイドルやっていけるのは\n{user}くんのおかげなんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should have more confidence in yourself.\nIt’s all thanks to {user} that I’m able to make it as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ yeah‚ great‚ thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "あーっ、本気にしてないなー！\n本当に感謝してるのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re not taking me seriously‚ are you?\nI’m being serious when I say I’m really thankful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　感謝のしるしとして何かプレゼントして\nあげようか？　何かほしいものある？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have an idea! I’ll give you a thank-you present!\nIs there anything that you want?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺と麻奈の出席日数……\nこのままだと俺達、卒業がヤバい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "School attendance days for me and you…\nAt this rate‚ we won’t be able to graduate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "そーいう現実的なことじゃなくて！\n出席日数もほしいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re thinking waaay too realistically!\nI mean‚ sure‚ attendance days would be nice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "現実的じゃなくて、俺がほしいもの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Way too realistic‚ huh… something that I want…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "分かった！　可愛い彼女だ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know! How about a cute girlfriend?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺に彼女が出来るのは現実的ではないのか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait… Are you saying it’s not realistic for me to have a girlfriend?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna010.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、残念\n私は、みんなのアイドルだから無理なんだよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh dear‚ what a shame.\nI’m an idol‚ so I belong to everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "俺の話、聞いてた？\n麻奈を彼女にしたいなんて、考えたことないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you even hear what I said?\nAnyway‚ I’ve never thought about dating you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna011.m4a",
      "text": "何それ、私はタイプじゃないってこと！？\nアッタマきた。問題発言だ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you saying I’m not your type?\nNOW I’m angry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルに恋愛感情を持つマネージャーの方が問題だろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A manager isn’t supposed to have romantic feelings for the idols they manage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna012.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうだけど……\nやっぱり納得いかない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right…\nBut I’m still not happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺にどうしろって言うんだよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What am I supposed to do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 113.5
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 113.5
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 115.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna013.m4a",
      "text": "んくっ、んくっ……\nあー！　レッスンの後の一杯は体に染みるよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*glug* *glug* *gulp*\nMmm! A cold one after a lesson feels so good!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 122.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "風呂上りにビール飲んでるオジさんみたいだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You sound like some middle-aged dad getting a beer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna014.m4a",
      "text": "つかまえて、失礼な！\nこんなに若くてかわいいアイドルを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To a young and pretty idol!\nWhat a rude thing to say!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 129.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna015.m4a",
      "text": "それに、これメロンソーダだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And this is cream soda‚ not beer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈は甘いジュースが好きなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You like sweet drinks?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 135.26666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-mna016.m4a",
      "text": "疲れてると甘いモノがほしくなるんだよ\nあ～、人工甘味料が染みる～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The human body craves sugar when it’s fatigued.\nOh‚ I love the taste of artificial flavoring…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 142.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "飲みながらでいいから、聞いてくれ\n次のライブのことなんだけど――",
      "translations": {
